'''蠕形螨属'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Demodex'''''}}），又称'''毛囊螨'''或'''毛囊虫'''，是[[蠕形螨科|蠕形螨科]]小型[[寄生|寄生]][[螨虫|螨虫]]的一個[[属_(生物)|属]]。
常寄生于[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]的毛囊内。目前已知蠕形螨有約65個種<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/notrocketscience/2012/08/31/everything-you-never-wanted-to-know-about-the-mites-that-eat-crawl-and-have-sex-on-your-face/#.UXeT_TcXekI |title=Everything you never wanted to know about the mites that eat, crawl, and have sex on your face |first=Ed |last=Yong |date=2012-08-31 |accessdate=2013-04-24 |language=en |department=Not Exactly Rocket Science |magazine=[[发现_(杂志)|Discover]] |archive-date=2019-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107094558/http://blogs.discovermagazine.com/notrocketscience/2012/08/31/everything-you-never-wanted-to-know-about-the-mites-that-eat-crawl-and-have-sex-on-your-face/#.UXeT_TcXekI |dead-url=no }}</ref>，140多个[[亚种|亚种]]；它们都是最小的[[节肢动物|节肢动物]]。目前已知有两种寄生于[[人类|人类]]：[[毛囊蠕形螨|毛囊蠕形螨]]与[[皮脂腺蠕形螨|皮脂腺蠕形螨]]，常被称作“睫毛螨”（''eyelash mites''）。蠕形螨的感染非常常见，几乎所有人类都有，患者一般也不会出现任何症状；蠕形螨偶尔会引发某些[[皮肤病|皮肤疾病]]。狗隻身上也有蟎蟲寄生。

==語源==
蠕形蟎屬的學名''Demodex''源自[[希臘語|希臘語]]的：{{lang|grc|''dēmos''}}（[[脂肪|脂肪]]）＋{{lang|grc|''dēx''}}（[[鞘翅目|木蟲]]）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://medicine.academic.ru/19095/Demodex | title = Demodex | work = Medical Dictionary (medicine.academic.ru) | access-date = 2016-01-12 | archive-date = 2020-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925012809/https://medicine.academic.ru/19095/Demodex | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==物種==
蠕形蟎屬是[[前氣門亞目|前氣門亞目]][[Eleutherengona|Eleutherengona]]下目[[Raphignathina|Raphignathina]]小目[[肉食蟎總科|肉食蟎總科]][[蠕形螨科|蠕形螨科]]之下七個屬之一<ref name="Zootaxa">{{cite book |first1=Zhi-Qiang |last1=Zhang |first2=Qing-Hai |last2=Fan |first3=Vladimir |last3=Pesic |first4=Harry |last4=Smit |first5=Andre V. |last5=Bochkov |first6=A. A. |last6=Khaustov |first7=Anne |last7=Baker |first8=Andreas |last8=Wohltmann |first9=Tinghuan |last9=Wen |first10=James W. |last10=Amrine |first11=P. |last11=Beron |first12=Jianzhen |last12=Lin |first13=Grzegorz |last13=Gabrys |first14=Robert |last14=Husband |chapter=Order '''Trombidiformes''' <small>Reuter, 1909</small> |chapterurl=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p138.pdf |url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |title=Animal biodiversity: An outline of higher-level classification and survey of taxonomic richness |editor=Zhang, Z.-Q. |journal=[[Zootaxa|Zootaxa]] |issue=3148 |year=2011 |pages=129-147 |publisher=[[Magnolia_Press|Magnolia Press]] |isbn=9781869778491 |language=en |access-date=2016-05-25 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222175509/http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/list/2011/3148.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，包括下列各個物種：
* [[大熊猫蠕形螨|大熊猫蠕形螨]] ''Demodex ailuropodae''<ref>徐业华, 谢禾秀, 刘素兰,等. 蠕形螨属一新种(真螨目:蠕形螨科)[J]. 动物学报, 1986(02):66-70.</ref>
* ''[[Demodex_aries|Demodex aries]]''
* ''[[Demodex_aurati|Demodex aurati]]''
* [[皮脂腺蠕形螨|皮脂腺蠕形螨]] ''Demodex brevis''
